{"tid":970488,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"阿媽逼選美　女神簡淑兒再揀多一次寧願去讀犯罪心理學","createTime":"2019-01-06T00:18:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-07T06:56:53.000Z","uid":12558,"like":2,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"638af2760c266ca4d1555e3741dffbc6f65c0308","tid":970488,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T00:18:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190104/mobile/bkn-20190104065049610-0104_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190104%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190104065049610-0104_00862_001.html&d=rCC6LyfnNA3Id4pBenNlAWMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=9dbef2e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190104/mobile/bkn-20190104065049610-0104_00862_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n藝人簡淑兒（Jessica）係參加選美入行，但參加原因竟然係因為媽媽想佢壯膽！回望6年前呢個決定，Jessica笑言如果畀佢再揀多一次，可能會試吓以其他途徑入行，例如參加藝訓班，不過，佢都好多謝媽媽咁樣逼一逼，令佢發現自己對娛樂圈係有好大興趣。 <br />\n<br />\n問到咁多年嚟覺得自己有咩進步？Jessica就話︰「以前做娛樂新聞主播會成日眨眼、講嘢又漏口咁，不停食螺絲，用咗好多時間去克服，自己又唔善於溝通，講嘢好直，以為自己講笑，但人哋聽起嚟感覺唔好，成日都好似得罪人咁。（性格關係到由細到大喺外國讀書？）係呀！啲人會覺得我扮鬼妹，因為我中文唔叻，但依家中文進步咗好多，會抽時間去搵老師練發音。」 <br />\n<br />\n談到讀書時期，原來Jessica係修讀心理學課程，仲話如果唔做藝人就會係想做犯罪心理學家，去幫助社會上有需要嘅人：「想令大家對呢一方面有多啲認識，不過要做專業人士就要繼續讀上去，暫時都仲未有呢個時間，自己好難去分心兼顧，又唔係天生讀書材料，純粹係好鍾意心理學，如果有日少啲幕前嘢就去讀番。」佢仲大爆爸爸知道佢要讀心理學，曾經嬲到拍枱叫佢唔好讀：「佢比較傳統，有問點解女仔之家讀埋呢啲，佢覺得犯人好危險，就會覺得點解要去接觸咁危險嘅人，佢哋上一輩同埋中國人傳統會覺得犯人係唔正常嘅人，但我個人覺得太多人誤解咗呢樣嘢。」 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hO5xwfy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhO5xwfy.png&h=4dc27791&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qZ5p6OU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqZ5p6OU.png&h=673e6f4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mcE2TtV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmcE2TtV.png&h=f60289b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sQGdfHf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsQGdfHf.png&h=61f0037d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kkQtO2g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkkQtO2g.png&h=5e814736&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3fampAC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3fampAC.png&h=e18774a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2U6EbfD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2U6EbfD.png&h=7d897e80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E1oOO2j.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE1oOO2j.png&h=06fd07aa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e840429363975fb67e0b3fcb459940a06e992a90","tid":970488,"uid":228143,"like":7,"dislike":23,"score":-16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T00:26:06.000Z","msg":"點解有d人咁屈機又有家境又讀得書又靚"},{"pid":"ab9523bbd9cd3cad46aef4830891177c980e27c4","tid":970488,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T01:30:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e3f392d15ec030b1ce01173e27f79fbe0cea34f","tid":970488,"uid":29523,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T01:32:40.000Z","msg":"幾時出3.0版？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5e4fe1229bb913d03c760a6fd71f6c8d9b71a9c","tid":970488,"uid":146435,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T01:35:38.000Z","msg":"讀完可以同高海寧一齊拍最新果集saw"},{"pid":"56a4940673149681a39e282fbe9145cf51892a32","tid":970488,"uid":27597,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T02:13:11.000Z","msg":"好樣衰"},{"pid":"10ea88c8634475a4d8e91b7b35b5d76a61b0d4b4","tid":970488,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-0